<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="pt-BR"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&amp;family=Hanken+Grotesk:wght@400;600;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
<script id="tailwind-config">
      tailwind.config = {
        darkMode: "class",
        theme: {
          extend: {
            "colors": {
                    "on-tertiary-fixed-variant": "#454748",
                    "on-error-container": "#93000a",
                    "surface-bright": "#f6faff",
                    "primary-container": "#00234b",
                    "inverse-on-surface": "#e9f2fb",
                    "tertiary-fixed-dim": "#c5c7c8",
                    "tertiary": "#0c0e0f",
                    "error": "#ba1a1a",
                    "tertiary-fixed": "#e1e3e4",
                    "surface-container-lowest": "#ffffff",
                    "outline": "#74777f",
                    "surface-variant": "#dbe4ed",
                    "outline-variant": "#c4c6d0",
                    "on-surface": "#141d23",
                    "inverse-surface": "#293138",
                    "surface-container-highest": "#dbe4ed",
                    "on-primary-fixed-variant": "#2c4771",
                    "background": "#f6faff",
                    "secondary": "#006d37",
                    "on-secondary": "#ffffff",
                    "surface-dim": "#d2dbe4",
                    "surface-container-high": "#e0e9f2",
                    "on-primary": "#ffffff",
                    "surface": "#f6faff",
                    "surface-tint": "#455f8a",
                    "on-secondary-fixed-variant": "#005228",
                    "inverse-primary": "#adc7f8",
                    "surface-container-low": "#ecf5fe",
                    "primary": "#000e24",
                    "on-primary-container": "#718bb9",
                    "primary-fixed": "#d6e3ff",
                    "on-surface-variant": "#43474e",
                    "on-primary-fixed": "#001b3d",
                    "secondary-container": "#6bfe9c",
                    "on-tertiary-container": "#898b8c",
                    "on-tertiary": "#ffffff",
                    "secondary-fixed-dim": "#4ae183",
                    "primary-fixed-dim": "#adc7f8",
                    "on-tertiary-fixed": "#191c1d",
                    "on-secondary-fixed": "#00210c",
                    "on-error": "#ffffff",
                    "tertiary-container": "#212425",
                    "surface-container": "#e6eff8",
                    "secondary-fixed": "#6bfe9c",
                    "on-background": "#141d23",
                    "error-container": "#ffdad6",
                    "on-secondary-container": "#00743a"
            },
            "borderRadius": {
                    "DEFAULT": "0.125rem",
                    "lg": "0.25rem",
                    "xl": "0.5rem",
                    "full": "0.75rem"
            },
            "spacing": {
                    "md": "16px",
                    "unit": "4px",
                    "xl": "32px",
                    "lg": "24px",
                    "gutter": "16px",
                    "xs": "4px",
                    "sidebar_width": "260px",
                    "sm": "8px",
                    "header_height": "64px"
            },
            "fontFamily": {
                    "title-sm": ["Inter"],
                    "body-md": ["Inter"],
                    "headline-md": ["Hanken Grotesk"],
                    "display-lg": ["Hanken Grotesk"],
                    "label-bold": ["Inter"],
                    "label-sm": ["Inter"],
                    "body-sm": ["Inter"]
            },
            "fontSize": {
                    "title-sm": ["18px", {"lineHeight": "24px", "fontWeight": "600"}],
                    "body-md": ["14px", {"lineHeight": "20px", "fontWeight": "400"}],
                    "headline-md": ["24px", {"lineHeight": "32px", "fontWeight": "600"}],
                    "display-lg": ["32px", {"lineHeight": "40px", "letterSpacing": "-0.02em", "fontWeight": "700"}],
                    "label-bold": ["12px", {"lineHeight": "16px", "fontWeight": "600"}],
                    "label-sm": ["11px", {"lineHeight": "14px", "fontWeight": "500"}],
                    "body-sm": ["13px", {"lineHeight": "18px", "fontWeight": "400"}]
            }
          },
        },
      }
    </script>
<style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        .font-headline-md, .font-display-lg { font-family: 'Hanken Grotesk', sans-serif; }
        .material-symbols-outlined {
            font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        /* Custom scrollbar for Windows aesthetic */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #f1f1f1; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #c4c6d0; border-radius: 4px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #74777f; }

        /* Sidebar Styles imported from home.html */
        :root {
            --sidebar-blue: #0b1421;
            --accent-green: #00a859;
            --text-white: #ffffff;
        }
        .sidebar { width: 260px; background-color: var(--sidebar-blue); color: var(--text-white); padding: 25px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; position: fixed; height: 100vh; left: 0; top: 0; box-sizing: border-box; z-index: 50; }
        .sidebar .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .sidebar .logo i { font-size: 28px; color: #90cdf4; }
        .sidebar .logo h2 { font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;}
        .sidebar .logo span { font-size: 10px; opacity: 0.6; }
        .sidebar .menu ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
        .sidebar .menu li { padding: 12px 15px; margin-bottom: 5px; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; opacity: 0.7; transition: 0.3s; font-size: 14px; display: block; }
        .sidebar .menu li:hover, .sidebar .menu li.active { background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); opacity: 1; }
        .sidebar .menu li i { margin-right: 12px; width: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .sidebar .sidebar-footer { margin-top: auto; }
        .sidebar .btn-new { width: 100%; background-color: var(--accent-green); color: white; border: none; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; cursor: pointer; }
        .sidebar .sidebar-footer ul { list-style: none; font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.7; padding: 0; }
        .sidebar .sidebar-footer li { margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
    <%- include('partials/sidebar_css') %>
</head>
<body class="bg-background text-on-background">
<!-- SideNavBar -->
<%- include('partials/sidebar') %>
<!-- TopNavBar Shell -->
<header class="h-header_height fixed top-0 right-0 left-sidebar_width bg-surface dark:bg-surface-dim border-b border-outline-variant flex justify-between items-center px-lg w-full z-10">
<div class="flex items-center">
<span class="font-title-sm text-title-sm text-primary font-bold mr-xl">Portal Administrativo</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-md">
<button class="p-2 hover:bg-surface-container-low rounded-full transition-colors text-on-surface-variant">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">notifications</span>
</button>
<button class="p-2 hover:bg-surface-container-low rounded-full transition-colors text-on-surface-variant">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">help_outline</span>
</button>
<div class="flex items-center gap-sm ml-md border-l border-outline-variant pl-md">
<div class="text-right">
<p class="font-label-bold text-label-bold text-primary">Admin Principal</p>
<p class="text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant">COORDENAÇÃO</p>
</div>
<img alt="Foto do Administrador" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-outline-variant object-cover" data-alt="A professional headshot of a school administrator in his late 40s, wearing a charcoal grey suit and a white shirt. The background is a blurred office environment with soft morning light filtering through a window, creating a warm and authoritative atmosphere. The visual style is clean and corporate, utilizing a high-key lighting setup that matches a modern educational management software interface." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDI2-9ks6C_8yPhICjOXUUXDemZw8tgLLo6AzUktEDpaXh32wBv7-ls1jyTz1giuA6Tz0QZSgORVaRVEztwnLh1ppcBgCuYuIQN-5NNA8GMO6vAVgrj9EjHzukAhTZS9KxhOMxw5Ine-imz4x6l9vLlGUU9FISzwfaATqkaMHvkj7sqfJXsMJidP1Wuf5BR4xEojc1Vum6URi2N_OmpAkXP6nFpQ3-F2s3A_ffmxKcdpxPt3DJXizTXo59lFMd0uWOBUNix1z11Tj7p"/>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<!-- Main Content Canvas -->
<main class="ml-sidebar_width pt-header_height min-h-screen bg-background">
<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto p-xl">
<!-- Header Section -->
<div class="mb-xl flex justify-between items-end">
<div>
<nav class="flex text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-unit">
<span>Alunos</span>
<span class="mx-xs">/</span>
<span class="text-primary font-bold">Novo Cadastro</span>
</nav>
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary">Cadastro de Aluno</h2>
<p class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Preencha as informações abaixo para matricular um novo estudante.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-sm">
<button class="px-lg py-2 border border-outline-variant text-primary font-label-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-all" onclick="window.location.href='/alunos'">Cancelar</button>
<button class="px-lg py-2 bg-primary text-on-primary font-label-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-container transition-all flex items-center gap-xs">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">save</span>
                        Cadastrar
                    </button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Main Form Card -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
<div class="p-lg border-b border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low flex items-center gap-sm">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">person_add</span>
<h3 class="font-title-sm text-title-sm text-primary">Informações Pessoais</h3>
</div>
<form class="p-xl space-y-lg">
<!-- Grid Layout for Personal Info -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-lg">
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-8">
<label class="block font-label-bold text-label-bold text-on-surface-variant mb-unit">Nome Completo</label>
<input class="w-full h-10 px-md border border-outline-variant rounded bg-white text-body-md focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all" placeholder="Ex: João Silva Santos" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4">
<label class="block font-label-bold text-label-bold text-on-surface-variant mb-unit">CPF</label>
<input class="w-full h-10 px-md border border-outline-variant rounded bg-white text-body-md focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all" placeholder="000.000.000-00" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4">
<label class="block font-label-bold text-label-bold text-on-surface-variant mb-unit">Data de Nascimento</label>
<input class="w-full h-10 px-md border border-outline-variant rounded bg-white text-body-md focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all" type="date"/>
</div>
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4">
<label class="block font-label-bold text-label-bold text-on-surface-variant mb-unit">Celular</label>
<input class="w-full h-10 px-md border border-outline-variant rounded bg-white text-body-md focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all" placeholder="(00) 00000-0000" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4">
<label class="block font-label-bold text-label-bold text-on-surface-variant mb-unit">E-mail</label>
<input class="w-full h-10 px-md border border-outline-variant rounded bg-white text-body-md focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all" placeholder="exemplo@email.com" type="email"/>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Address Section Divider -->
<div class="flex items-center gap-md py-md">
<span class="font-label-bold text-label-bold text-primary whitespace-nowrap uppercase tracking-wider">Endereço de Residência</span>
<div class="h-px bg-outline-variant w-full"></div>
</div>
<!-- Grid Layout for Address -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-lg">
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3">
<label class="block font-label-bold text-label-bold text-on-surface-variant mb-unit">CEP</label>
<input class="w-full h-10 px-md border border-outline-variant rounded bg-white text-body-md focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all" placeholder="00000-000" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-7">
<label class="block font-label-bold text-label-bold text-on-surface-variant mb-unit">Logradouro</label>
<input class="w-full h-10 px-md border border-outline-variant rounded bg-white text-body-md focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all" placeholder="Rua, Avenida, Praça..." type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-2">
<label class="block font-label-bold text-label-bold text-on-surface-variant mb-unit">Número</label>
<input class="w-full h-10 px-md border border-outline-variant rounded bg-white text-body-md focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all" placeholder="123" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4">
<label class="block font-label-bold text-label-bold text-on-surface-variant mb-unit">Bairro</label>
<input class="w-full h-10 px-md border border-outline-variant rounded bg-white text-body-md focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all" placeholder="Digite o bairro" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-5">
<label class="block font-label-bold text-label-bold text-on-surface-variant mb-unit">Cidade</label>
<input class="w-full h-10 px-md border border-outline-variant rounded bg-white text-body-md focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all" placeholder="Ex: São Paulo" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3">
<label class="block font-label-bold text-label-bold text-on-surface-variant mb-unit">Estado (UF)</label>
<select class="w-full h-10 px-md border border-outline-variant rounded bg-white text-body-md focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all">
<option value="">Selecione</option>
<option value="SP">São Paulo</option>
<option value="RJ">Rio de Janeiro</option>
<option value="MG">Minas Gerais</option>
<option value="PR">Paraná</option>
</select>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Form Footer Buttons -->
<div class="pt-xl flex justify-end gap-md">
<button class="px-xl py-3 text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary font-label-bold transition-colors" type="reset">Limpar Campos</button>
<button class="px-xl py-3 bg-secondary text-on-secondary rounded-lg font-label-bold shadow-md hover:bg-on-secondary-fixed-variant active:scale-95 transition-all flex items-center gap-sm" type="submit">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
                            Confirmar Cadastro
                        </button>
</div>
</form>
</div>
<!-- Auxiliary Information Cards (Bento Style) -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-lg mt-xl">
<div class="bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed p-lg rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-between border border-primary/10">
<div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined mb-sm">info</span>
<h4 class="font-label-bold text-label-bold">Dica do Sistema</h4>
</div>
<p class="text-body-sm mt-sm">O preenchimento do CPF é obrigatório para a emissão automática de boletos e certificados.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-high border border-outline-variant p-lg rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-between">
<div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined mb-sm text-primary">verified_user</span>
<h4 class="font-label-bold text-label-bold text-primary">Segurança de Dados</h4>
</div>
<p class="text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant mt-sm">Este sistema está em conformidade com a LGPD. Todos os dados são criptografados.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container p-lg rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-between border border-secondary/10">
<div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined mb-sm">support_agent</span>
<h4 class="font-label-bold text-label-bold">Precisa de Ajuda?</h4>
</div>
<p class="text-body-sm mt-sm">Contate o suporte técnico no ramal 404 para dúvidas sobre documentação acadêmica.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<footer class="mt-auto py-lg text-center border-t border-outline-variant">
<p class="text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">© 2024 EduManage v4.2.1 • Sistema de Gestão Acadêmica Integrada</p>
</footer>
</main>
</body></html>